short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to assist with navigating many tabs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hundreds of open tabs can quickly become overwhelming when searching for a webpage you had open or trying to locate all the tabs relating to one specific domain or subject. Tablisto reduces this to a quick and effortless way of visualizing and filtering the multiple tabs and Chrome browser windows.
